      <section eId="sec_71_2201">
        <num>71-2201</num>
        <heading>Enforcement of title 23 of article 23 of this chapter</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2201__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of subdivision one of section\n23-2307 or paragraph</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_71_2201__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of subdivision two of section 23-2307 of this\nchapter shall be liable for a civil penalty of not more than five\nhundred dollars, and an additional civil penalty of not more than five\nhundred dollars for each day during which such violation continues, not\nto exceed ten thousand dollars.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
